气象部门在飓风经过期间进行的地面观测很少，但官方报告中认为墨西哥南部所受影响最为严重。风暴登陆点附近的瓦哈卡州[[埃斯孔迪多港_(瓦哈卡州)|埃斯孔迪多港]]在宝莲来袭数小时前就测得每小时115公里的阵风时速，由于此后当地没有再记录下有效风速数值，所以这也是陆地上测得的最强阵风。阿卡普尔科的一个[[风速计|风速计]]测得每小时75公里的持续风速和95公里的阵风时速，虽然上述数值都低于飓风标准，但官方估计气旋途经该地区时可能仍有飓风强度。<ref name="tcr" />风暴沿途暴降暴雨<ref name="cnn108a" />，许多地区的降雨量超过381毫米。据[[墨西哥国家气象局|墨西哥国家水资源委员会]]提供的数据，有2132处地点测得降水。降雨量最高的两地分别是圣路易斯阿克兰（{{lang|en|San Luis Actlan}}，688毫米）和普恩特胡拉（{{lang|en|Puente Jula}}，930毫米）<ref name="cnn108a" /><ref>{{cite web | author = David Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2007 | title = Hurricane Pauline - October 3-October 10, 1997 | format = GIF | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140721033713/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/pauline1997.html | archivedate = 2014-07-21 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/pauline1997.html}}</ref>，创下格雷罗州历史上热带气旋降雨量的新纪录<ref name="Roth">{{cite web |author = David Roth | title = Tropical Cyclone Maxima Per Mexican State | format = GIF | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmexicostatemaxima.gif | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | archivedate = 2013-05-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130530225227/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmexicostatemaxima.gif}}</ref>。飓风24小时里就在阿卡普尔科降下430毫米雨量，刷新该市1974年创下的纪录<ref name="your dad">{{cite web | title = Efectos del huracán "Pauline" (1997) sobre la fauna asociada a la planta Eichhornia crassipes en la Laguna Coyuca, Pacífico Sur de México | url = http://www.ots.ac.cr/tropiweb/attachments/volumes/vol56-2/16-Roman-Efectos.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120614172057/http://www.ots.ac.cr/tropiweb/attachments/volumes/vol56-2/16-Roman-Efectos.pdf | publisher = Laboratorio de Carcinoparasitología, Instituto de Ciencias del Mar y Limnología, Universidad Nacional Autónoma de México (UNAM) | accessdate = 2012-06-14 | date = 2007-05 | archivedate = 2012-06-14 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，并且4小时的降雨量就高达350毫米，相当于该市年均降雨量的四分之一<ref>{{cite journal | author = R. Meli | title = Damage in Acapulco by Hurricane Pauline | date = 1998-03 | journal = Natural Hazards Observer | volume = 22 | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://www.colorado.edu/hazards/o/archives/1998/mar98/mar98a.html#acapulco | issue = 4 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141003022154/http://www.colorado.edu/hazards/o/archives/1998/mar98/mar98a.html#acapulco | archivedate = 2014-10-03 }}</ref>。飓风登陆期间，瓦哈卡州海岸沿线出现约9米高的狂浪<ref name="cnn108a" />。

宝莲对恰帕斯州的影响很小，但墨西哥最穷困的瓦哈卡州和格雷罗州受到重创。最影响最重的是阿卡普尔科及其周边地区<ref name="rw1">{{cite web | author = Church World Service | year = 1997 | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824135149/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/situation-report-hurricane-pauline | deadurl = no | title = Situation Report Hurricane Pauline | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/situation-report-hurricane-pauline}}</ref>。墨西哥一共因这场飓风遭受了价值4亿4780万美元（1997年[[美元|美元]]）的损失<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Université catholique de Louvain | location = Brussels – Belgium | title = EM-DAT: The OFDA/CRED International Disaster Database | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://www.emdat.be/database | archive-date = 2016-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160906135830/http://www.emdat.be/database | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[联合国|联合国]]人道主义事务部分发布的报告中称，风暴过去3天后，当地已确认有137人遇难<ref name="rw4">{{cite web | author = United Nations Department of Humanitarian Affairs | year = 1997 | title = Mexico Hurricane Pauline Situation Report No.1 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-hurricane-pauline-situation-report-no1 | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824135920/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-hurricane-pauline-situation-report-no1}}</ref>。飓风过去4天后，[[路透社|路透社]]在新闻报道中称死亡人数上升到173，另有200人失踪<ref name="rwplague">{{cite news | author = David Luhnow | date = 1997-10-13 | title = Plague Fears Mount in Storm-Wrecked Acapulco | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824140851/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/plague-fears-mount-storm-wrecked-acapulco | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/plague-fears-mount-storm-wrecked-acapulco | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = no | publisher = Reuters | accessdate = 2015-08-24}}</ref>，墨西哥政府则发布声明，称有149人丧生<ref name="rw5">{{cite web | author = Australian Broadcasting Corporation | year = 1997 | title = Survivors of Mexican hurricane facing shortages of food and water | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/survivors-mexican-hurricane-facing-shortages-food-and-water | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | archivedate = 2021-04-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411114951/https://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/survivors-mexican-hurricane-facing-shortages-food-and-water }}</ref>。最终，媒体报道估计至少有230人死亡，墨西哥[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]则估计有400人丧生<ref name="tcr" />，至少1900人失踪。[[教会世界服务社|教会世界服务社]]估计有至少500人遇难<ref name="rw1016">{{cite web | author = Church World Service | year = 1997 | title = Situation Report Hurricane Pauline | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/situation-report-hurricane-pauline-0 | archive-date = 2021-04-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411114953/https://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/situation-report-hurricane-pauline-0 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[全球救援网|全球救援网]]认为，死亡人数应为217，共有60万人受灾<ref name="Interragate.com">{{cite web | title = Hurricane Pauline - October 1997, Mexico | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20070729074031/http://www.interragate.info/notable-past-event/3855 | url = http://www.interragate.info/notable-past-event/3855 | publisher = Interragate.com | accessdate = 2007-07-29 | author = Administrator | date = 2007-02-18 | archivedate = 2007-07-29 }}</ref>。约有30万人因风暴流离失所<ref name="Relief Web reports">{{cite web | title = Initial Disaster Appeal Mexico Hurricane Pauline | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/initial-disaster-appeal-mexico-hurricane-pauline | publisher = Relief Web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824142310/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/initial-disaster-appeal-mexico-hurricane-pauline | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | date = 1997-10-24}}</ref>。

=== 环境 ===
飓风对环境构成严重破坏，墨西哥南部有700平方公里位于低洼地区的[[雨林|雨林]]、松林和常绿栎林受到重创<ref name="fao">{{cite web | author = North American Forest Commission | year = 1998 | title = Impact of climatic factors such as El Niño on forests | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://www.fao.org/UNFAO/Bodies/NAFC/nafc98/NAFC4-E.HTM | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141112012222/http://www.fao.org/UNFAO/Bodies/NAFC/nafc98/NAFC4-E.HTM | archivedate = 2014-11-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。强烈的海浪导致部分地点出现严重海滩[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]，这种侵蚀又对[[丽龟|丽龟]]的巢穴构成重大影响<ref name="turtle">{{cite web | author = Laura Sarti, Juan Díaz, Manuel Garduño, Javier Vasconcelos, Ernesto Albavera, Cuauhtemoc Peñaflores, and René Márquez M. | year = 1998 | title = Effect of Hurricane Pauline on the Nesting of Olive Ridley Turtle in Escobilla Beach, Oaxaca, Mexico | publisher = United States Department of Commerce | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/pdfs/species/turtlesymposium1998.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121010203058/http://www.nmfs.noaa.gov/pr/pdfs/species/turtlesymposium1998.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-10 | format = PDF}}</ref>，有约4000万枚蛋被毁。约80万6000个巢穴受到影响，其中约半数被海水席卷一空<ref name="egg">{{cite web | author = Marine Turtle Newsletter | year = 1997 | title = Hurricane Pauline Destroyed 40 Million Sea Turtle Eggs in the Oaxacan Beach of Mazunte | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://www.seaturtle.org/mtn/archives/mtn78/mtn78p26.shtml | archive-date = 2013-04-15 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20130415194113/http://www.seaturtle.org/mtn/archives/mtn78/mtn78p26.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。飓风宝莲是继[[1959年墨西哥飓风|1959年]]以来袭击墨西哥南部的最强飓风，也是最致命的飓风<ref name="rw2">{{cite web | author = Action by Churches Together International | title = Alert Mexico Hurricane Pauline | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/alert-mexico-hurricane-pauline | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824150659/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/alert-mexico-hurricane-pauline | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-08-24}}</ref>，此外，这还是有纪录以来首场吹袭太平洋[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]的飓风<ref>{{cite journal | title = First documented hurricane strikes on eastern Pacific coral reefs reveal only slight damage | url = http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs003380050140 | author = P.W. Glynn, D. Lirman, A.C. Baker and G.E. Leyte Morales | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | format = PDF | volume = 17 | issue = 4, 368 | doi = 10.1007/s003380050140 | year = 1998 | journal = Coral Reefs | page = 368 | archive-date = 2021-04-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210413195956/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s003380050140 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。墨西哥的农作物也受到重创，损失了约40万袋咖啡。飓风过去后，大豆和小麦价格都出现上涨<ref>{{cite news | title = Solid export demands take soybeans, wheat prices higher | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=B_xfAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DlcMAAAAIBAJ&pg=6485,2819817&dq=hurricane+pauline+1+billion&hl=en | accessdate = 2011-10-09 | newspaper = The Robesonian | date = 1997-10-10 | archive-date = 2021-04-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210413195959/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=B_xfAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DlcMAAAAIBAJ&pg=6485,2819817&dq=hurricane+pauline+1+billion&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。除此以外，飓风宝莲还对墨西哥南部的动物有很大影响<ref name="your dad" />。

=== 瓦哈卡州 ===
气旋登陆后不久，瓦哈卡州宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="cnn109">{{cite news | author = CNN | year = 1997 | title = Pauline hits Mexico's Pacific coast resorts | accessdate = 2007-01-10 | archivedate = 2005-04-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050420122959/http://www.cnn.com/WEATHER/9710/09/pauline/ | url = http://www.cnn.com/WEATHER/9710/09/pauline/}}</ref>。过量降水导致河流溢出，全州有50个[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]]被淹。洪水令12座桥梁受损<ref name="rw4" />，其中两座被毁<ref name="rw1013">{{cite web | author = UN Department of Public Information | year = 1997 | title = Mexican states of Oaxaca and Guerrero ask UNICEF for assistance following destruction by hurricane Pauline | accessdate = 2015-08-25 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexican-states-oaxaca-and-guerrero-ask-unicef-assistance-following-destruction | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824152015/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexican-states-oaxaca-and-guerrero-ask-unicef-assistance-following-destruction}}</ref>，部分地区的供电、饮用水和电信服务中断了数天<ref name="rw4" />。飓风途经之处有数以千计的房屋受损，导致该州约25万人无家可归<ref name="table">{{cite web | author = National Drought Mitigation Center | accessdate = 2011-07-20 | url = http://drought.unl.edu/risk/world/table2.pdf | year = 1997 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110720093259/http://www.drought.unl.edu/risk/world/table2.pdf | title = Reported Effects of the 1997-98 El Niño | archivedate = 2011-07-20 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF}}</ref>。瓦哈卡州至少有110人丧生，数十万居民和1278个社区受到影响<ref name="rw1016" />。

瓦哈卡州南部各地都有树木被宝莲产生的大风刮倒，多条输电线缆中断。安赫尔港和一处海军基地一度同外界失联。瓦图尔科当地电视台的天线被风刮倒，还有至少30套纸板房屋被毁<ref name="cnn108a" />。该市机场附近的一个社区受到重创，导致多人流离失所。风暴产生的暴雨在瓦哈卡州和邻近的恰帕斯州部分地区引发严重洪灾<ref name="cnn109" />。全州共有约500个社区被彻底摧毁，受灾最严重的地区包括[[萨波特克人|萨波特克]]、[[查蒂诺人|查蒂诺]]和[[米斯特克|米斯特克]]<ref name="rw1016" />。

=== 格雷罗州 ===
[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]南部各地因暴雨引发严重的[[泥石流|泥石流]]和洪灾。多个社区几乎被完全摧毁，其中部分社区的洪水在飓风过去数周后仍未退去。洪水冲走或摧毁了数千英亩农作物，还导致数千头牛死亡。超过4万5000人因洪水和泥石流而失去同外界的联系。<ref name="rw1016" />飓风途经之地有许多房屋、桥梁以及供电和供水设施受损<ref name="table" />。阿卡普尔科在3小时里就降下约400毫米雨量，导致多条河流泛滥。阿卡普尔科港有约1100艘船滞留，35艘船沉没。该州单咖啡产业就蒙受了8000万美元损失。<ref name="your mom">{{cite web | title = Algunos efectos de la precipitación del huracán Paulina en Acapulco, Guerrero | publisher = Investigaciones Geográfica | author = Boletín 37 | pages = 1–14 | url = http://www.igeograf.unam.mx/sigg/utilidades/docs/pdfs/publicaciones/inves_geo/boletines/37/b37_art262.pdf | format = PDF | date = 1998-04-04 | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924033207/http://www.igeograf.unam.mx/sigg/utilidades/docs/pdfs/publicaciones/inves_geo/boletines/37/b37_art262.pdf | archive-date = 2015-09-24 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>某环保机构估算，当地的咖啡作物需要15年才能恢复。据初步估算，格雷罗州共有123人遇难，其中大部分<ref name="rw4" />生活在阿卡普尔科。飓风过去4天后，仍有超过200人失踪，有些被卷入大海，有些则被埋在泥石流下<ref name="rw5" />。全州共有5万人流离失所<ref name="table" />。[[热带风暴奥拉夫_(1997年)|热带风暴奥拉夫]]在一周前刚刚吹袭当地，土壤中的含水量本就处于基本饱和状态，再加上宝莲产生的降水，导致阿卡普尔科周边的[[棚户区|棚户区]]遭遇严重的泥石流和山洪爆发<ref name="rw3">{{cite web | author = International Red Cross and Red Crescent Movement | year = 1997 | title = Mexico Hurricane Pauline Information Bulletin No.1 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824160327/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-hurricane-pauline-information-bulletin-no1 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-hurricane-pauline-information-bulletin-no1}}</ref>。当地约有5000套房屋被毁，另外2万5000套受损<ref name="rw1016" />，阿卡普尔科市内及周边有1万人无家可归<ref name="rw1" />。靠近海滩的豪华度假酒店很大程度上得以躲过一劫，但生活在棚户区的许多居民则失去了仅有的家当。阿卡普尔科大部分区域被泥浆覆盖，全城70%的地区在飓风过后失去供水<ref name="rwplague" />。全城100万居民中大部分都失去供电和电话服务<ref name="rw1" />。全州遭受的经济损失达近3亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]<ref name="your mom" />。

== 善后 ==
[[File:Acapulco_-_PlacaPaulina2.JPG|right]]
墨西哥红十字会的志愿者和搜救队一起迅速赶赴灾区<ref name="rw3" />，还采用经过专门训练的狗在阿卡普尔科寻找因飓风而被困在泥泞之下的灾民。风暴过去的前4天里，每支搜救队每天都会找到1到2具尸体，官方估计搜救工作需要持续数周<ref name="rwplague" />。搜救队在[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]一共救出35人<ref name="rw4" />。飓风过去仅数小时后，救灾人员就乘船进入洪灾地区，向受灾最严重的区域提供援助。红十字会向在瓦哈卡州、格雷罗州和恰帕斯州政府开设避难所中躲避的灾民提供食品、水、衣物、毛毯、净水物品、奶粉及其他不易腐烂变质的食品和医疗物资。墨西哥红十字会还设立多个避难所，为数以百计流留失所的灾民提供住宿和饮食。风暴过去4天后，红十字会已经向飓风灾民发放100[[公吨|吨]]救灾物资。另外还有多名医务工作者被派往当地救治伤者。<ref name="rw3" />

官员在阿卡普尔科设立应急水质净化厂，但大部分用水需求仍然无法满足。运水车陆续开往市内，有成千上万的人排队取水。该市豪华酒店内的游客大部分没有受到这场飓风的影响，<ref name="rwplague" />这些酒店很快就恢复正常，但市内其他地方仍然满目疮痍<ref name="usa today">{{cite news | title = Acapulco tourist area rebounds from Pauline | newspaper = USA Today | date = 1997-10-17 | author = Gene Sloan | location = McLean, Virginia | pages = 01.D}}</ref>。多家酒店被迫使用瓶装水，尽可能少使用配给水，以便将有限的水提供给市内其他地区<ref name="reuters1015">{{cite news | author = David Luhnow | date = 1997-10-15 | title = Mexico Storm Victims Desperate for Food, Water | publisher = Reuters | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-storm-victims-desperate-food-water | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918120641/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-storm-victims-desperate-food-water | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-09-18}}</ref>。飓风过去后，阿卡普尔科出现严重的[[哄抬物价|哄抬物价]]情况，据消费者保护机构的正式报告显示，店主将牛奶价格抬高了200%，玉米饼则有500%，水更达1000%<ref name="rw5" />。墨西哥政府因预警不足和水资源短缺受到批评，当时的[[墨西哥总统|墨西哥总统]][[埃內斯托·柴迪洛|埃內斯托·柴迪洛]]缩短他在欧洲的假期，对灾害作出响应<ref name="Economst.com">{{cite news | title = The lesson of hurricane Pauline | url = http://www.economist.com/node/102891 | work = The Americans print edition | publisher = Economist.com | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | date = 1997-10-16 | archive-date = 2017-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171020130242/http://www.economist.com/node/102891 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。政府官员为阿卡普尔科市民开设了39个救助中心，但还是有部分市民缺食少水。部分市民怀疑总统及其所属的[[革命制度党|革命制度党]]将救灾物资挪作他用。总统承诺会对相关责任人提出起诉，并且决定关闭救助中心，开设供应汤汁的厨房。虽然有了食品，但墨西哥军队没有出动设置厨房，也没有在救助中心发放援助物资。<ref name="reuters1015" />

宝莲过去1周后，阿卡普尔科大部分地区依旧处于封闭状态<ref name="reuters1015" />。该市有关部门起初优先清理旅游区，从酒店到机场间的景区公路因此很快就得以修复。风暴过后，前往当地旅游的人数大减，部分酒店为吸引客源降价40%。某航空公司还将[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]到阿卡普尔科的机票价格减半。宝莲过去约1个月后，大部分酒店都已完全恢复到正常水平。<ref name="nytimes119">{{cite news | author = Julia Preston | date = 1997-11-09 | title = Acapulco Tourist Areas Are Open After Storm | publisher = The New York Times | accessdate = 2015-08-25 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1997/11/09/travel/travel-advisory-acapulco-tourist-areas-are-open-after-storm.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150527055053/http://www.nytimes.com/1997/11/09/travel/travel-advisory-acapulco-tourist-areas-are-open-after-storm.html | archivedate = 2015-05-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

=== 捐助 ===
瓦哈卡州和格雷罗州政府向[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]请求援助，并以水箱、水泵和建筑材料最为急需<ref name="rw4" />。国际援助起初几乎完全聚焦于阿卡普尔科，飓风过去1周后，瓦哈卡州还有500个社区与外界隔绝，没有得到援助，格雷罗州也有多个大型社区存在同类情况<ref name="rw1016" />。[[基督复临发展救济局|基督复临发展救济局]]将7吨食品和衣物连同40人用客车送往与世隔绝的墨西哥南部村落<ref name="adra">{{cite web | author = Adventist Development and Relief Agency International | year = 1997 | title = Relief continues for hurricane survivors | accessdate = 2015-08-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918120730/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/relief-continues-hurricane-survivors | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/relief-continues-hurricane-survivors | archivedate = 2012-09-18}}</ref>。飓风过去约10天后，约2万人仍然无法获得救援人员协助，总统因此担心会开始有居民饿死。起初还有直升机被派往边远地区，但风暴之后的大雾和暴雨导致行动受阻。政府竭力将食品送往边远山区，但也有官员指出，这样的做法存在很大风险。<ref name="abc1019">{{cite web | author = Australian Broadcasting Corporation | date = 1997-10-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918120802/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/people-mexicos-pacific-mountains-face-starvation-after-hurricane | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/people-mexicos-pacific-mountains-face-starvation-after-hurricane | title = People in Mexico's Pacific mountains face starvation after hurricane | accessdate = 2015-08-25 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-09-18}}</ref>

宝莲过去3天后。[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]送出首批共2万5000美元捐款，还捐出塑料布充当临时屋顶，另有包括拖把、扫帚、水桶、海绵、漂白剂和清洁化学品在内的多种清洁用品<ref name="rw3" />。红十字会多个地方分会也伸出援手，[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[圣安东尼奥_(德克萨斯州)|圣安东尼奥]]分会送出清洁用品，[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]分会送出2000套安抚用品套装，其中除卫生用品外，还有为孩子们准备的填字游戏<ref name="arc">{{cite web | author = American Red Cross | year = 1997 | title = Hard Work Continues in the Wake of Hurricane Pauline | accessdate = 2015-08-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918120711/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hard-work-continues-wake-hurricane-pauline | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hard-work-continues-wake-hurricane-pauline | archivedate = 2012-09-18}}</ref>。德国红十字会同样提供了援助<ref name="rw3" />。

=== 疾病 ===
飓风产生的洪水同墨西哥西南部许多贫困地区未经处理的污水结合，致使大面积地区面临热带疾病传播的威胁。为此，政府卫生部门在格雷罗州和瓦哈卡州海岸沿线多个城市开设疫苗接种中心。数千人接种了[[伤寒|伤寒]]和[[破伤风|破伤风]]疫苗。政府部门警告，由于水质受到污染，还有可能爆发[[骨痛热症|登革热]]和[[霍乱|霍乱]]疫情。卫生部门表示，大面积的积水很可能滋生[[蚊|蚊虫]]，传播[[疟疾|疟疾]]和登革热。阿卡普尔斯在飓风过去两天后首见天晴，这也是当地一周以来第一个晴天，积水蒸发后，大量灰尘带着致命的病毒四处扩散。有关部门警告市民，受这些灰尘的威胁，食物和水要煮沸30分钟才能食用。<ref name="rwplague" />当地报告有至少20起霍乱<ref name="nytimes119" />和6起登革热病例<ref name="reuters1014">{{cite web | author = David Luhnow | date = 1997-10-14 | title = Cholera Breaks Out in Acapulco | publisher = Reuters | accessdate = 2015-08-25 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/cholera-breaks-out-acapulco | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918120655/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/cholera-breaks-out-acapulco | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-09-18}}</ref>。最为严重的疫情发生在瓦哈卡州，共计616个村落出现1万4630例疟疾病例，占墨西哥1998年疟疾病例总数的约80%<ref>{{cite journal | author = Juan E Hernández-Avila, et al. | year = 2006-09 / 2006-10 | title = Determinant factors for malaria transmission on the coast of Oaxaca State, the main residual transmission focus in Mexico | journal = Salud Pública de México | accessdate = 2011-11-03 | doi = 10.1590/S0036-36342006000500007 | volume = 48 | issue = 5 | page = 405 | url = http://www.scielosp.org/scielo.php?pid=S0036-36342006000500007&script=sci_arttext&tlng=es | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120405125528/http://www.scielosp.org/scielo.php?pid=S0036-36342006000500007&script=sci_arttext&tlng=es | archivedate = 2012-04-05 }}</ref>。军方分发[[氯|氯]]片为水池消毒，还用手推车从受损的民宅中清理腐烂的泥浆和污水。两架[[C-130运输机|C-130运输机]]和20架直升机将食品和水空运到阿卡普尔科以南的小村庄，这些地方的居民在风暴过后已经被困了近一星期。<ref name="reuters1015" />

=== 除名 ===
飓风宝莲过去不到1个月后，[[1997年飓风里克|飓风里克]]又吹袭了几乎同一地区，产生降水的同时也令救灾工作受阻，但其破坏程度相对宝莲而言很轻<ref name="Australia Severe Weather">{{cite web | author = Gary Padgett | year = 1997 | title = Monthly Global Tropical Cyclone Summary: November, 1997 | accessdate = 2015-08-25 | publisher = Australia Severe Weather | url = http://australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/1998/summ9711.htm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710073652/http://australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/1998/summ9711.htm | archivedate = 2015-07-10}}</ref>。1998年春，[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]决定将“宝莲”这一名称除名，今后永远不会再在[[太平洋颶風季|东太平洋风暴]]命名时采用<ref>{{cite web | author = Gary Padgett, Jack Beven, and James Lewis Free | title = Subject: B3) What names have been retired in the Atlantic and East Pacific basin? | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Hurricane Research Division | accessdate = 2015-08-25 | archivedate = 2015-03-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150327070031/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html}}</ref>。用于取代的新名称是“帕特里夏”（{{lang|en|Patricia}}），于[[2003年太平洋颶風季|2003年飓风季]]首度采用<ref name=ATWC>{{cite web | accessdate = 2012-07-21 | title = EASTERN NORTH PACIFIC TROPICAL CYCLONE NAME HISTORY | publisher = Atlantic Tropical Weather Center | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20120721160310/http://www.atwc.org/pachist.txt | url = http://www.atwc.org/pachist.txt | archivedate = 2012-07-21 | deadurl = yes | format = [[TXT|TXT]] }}</ref>。

